# WPIS bots rules

- **Layout**: `wpis-bot-mastodon/` and `wpis-bot-bluesky/` are separate plugin roots; shared code in `lib/`.
- **Dependency**: requires [**wpis-plugin**](https://github.com/jaz-on/wpis-plugin) active (quotes CPT, `wpis_find_potential_duplicates`, counter sync). Ingestion uses `wpis_submit_quote_candidate()` from core.
- **Docs**: ship with `docs/` in this repo (admin guide, API limits). Workspace mirror: `workspace/docs/wpis-bots/README.md`.
- **English copy**: workspace `.cursor/rules/no-oxford-comma-english.mdc` for user-facing strings.
